ere with all the on-the-ground retail, shopping, and trend observations you=
 need to track=E2=80=94including the story of an independent, family-owned =
department store chain that=E2=80=99s not only surviving, but, dare I say,
thriving? Up top, I share Milan Fashion Week=E2=80=99s latest, from Paul An=
drew=E2=80=99s debut at Sergio Rossi to Donatella Versace=E2=80=99s unleash=
ing. Plus, Sarah makes sense of these China tariffs, and also has an update=
