=C2=A0

On the Saks returns drama: =E2=80=9CThis might be a luxury sector peculiari=
ty, but I=E2=80=99m surprised that Saks processes its own returns=E2=80=94s=
o much so that
I found some return labels on GIS just to double check they weren=E2=80=99t=
