r like Inmar Intelligence, precisely because trying to do it in-house has s=
o many QA and efficiency issues. Maybe the product is valuable enough that =
they don=E2=80=99t want it in a third-party warehouse even briefly=E2=80=94=
it looks like N.M. also processed their own as recently as 2018ish, based o=
n some old job listings for processors. Whatever the reasoning, I=E2=80=99m=
